result.reason: Issue lacks reproduction details (mRemoteNG version, error message, RDP security/NLA settings used) needed to diagnose why Linux Hyper-V Enhanced Session RDP fails in mRemoteNG but works in RDCman.
result.approach: Ask reporter for exact error shown, mRemoteNG version, and RDP settings (Security, NLA, Network Level Auth) — likely a security negotiation mismatch (NLA vs Classic RDP) that can be fixed by exposing or adjusting the RDP AuthenticationLevel/NegotiateSecurityLayer properties in the RDP ActiveX control setup.
